data.description:
Property Faces East to West. The entrance is by the patio (12x14) on the East side of the home. Directly, on the right, is the greatroom,kitchenette and kitchen; to the lft of the entrance is the hall way leading to the second and third bedrooms, the fulll bathroom is to the right of the hall way.  Secondary and 3rd bathroom has a doulbe sink granit top. This bathroom has a double door entry into the secondary bedroom. The kitchen, greatroom, and full bathroom are ceramic tile cover, to include the hallway leading to the secondary and 3rd bedroom. The secondary bedroom is carpet covered and the 3rd bedroom is engineered wood covered. Stairwell leading to the Primary bedroom is carpet covered.
The primary bedroom is carpet covered. The primary bedroom has a walk-through bathroom headed into a walk-in closet. 

The upper-patio deck is partly covered by a wood-frame pergola. The upper patio is on the East side of the home.
